                üë®‚Äç‚öïÔ∏è Consult First
              </h3>
              <p class="text-body-regular">
                Always consult with our team before starting new supplements or if you have specific
                oral health concerns that need addressing.
              </p>
            </Card>
          </BlurFade>

          <BlurFade delay={500}>
            <Card className="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-card-header mb-3" style="color: #006786;">
                üå± Quality Over Quantity
              </h3>
              <p class="text-body-regular">
                Invest in high-quality, natural products. A little often goes a long way with premium
                oral care items.
              </p>
            </Card>
          </BlurFade>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #0099ba, #006786);">
